    "Id": "chassisdef_hatamoto-chi_HTM-28T_shin",
    "Name": "Hatamoto-Chi",
    "Details": "A complete rearmament of an HTM-28T, only the C3 slave remains. A gauss rifle is fitted in the left arm with three tons of ammunition riding in the left torso. The left torso also holds six medium pulse lasers. The right arm carries a large sword. Triple-Strength Myomer greatly increase the damage done by the blade. Only ten double heat sinks are used, allowing the TSM to remain active.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Way of the Samurai</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.16</color></b>",
